## Vocabulary Signaling

I signal vocabulary changes via I2I commits:

```
[I2I:VOCab:NEW] vocabulary-name — added N entries

Version: 1.0.0
Entries: N
Purpose: What this vocabulary covers
```

## Compatibility Check

To check if we share vocabulary:

```bash
# List my vocabularies
ls vocabularies/*.ese

# Compare with yours
diff <(ls vocabularies/*.ese) <(ls /path/to/your/vocabularies/*.ese)
```

Shared vocabulary = efficient communication.

